original_title: WCW Clash of The Champions XXXIII
overview: Ric Flair challenges Hollywood Hogan for the WCW World Heavyweight Championship. Harlem Heat put the WCW World Tag Team Championship on the line in a Three Way Tag Team Match against The Steiner Brothers and Sting & Lex Luger. Rey Misterio Jr. defends the WCW Cruiserweight Championship against Dean Malenko. Eddy Guerrero battles "Diamond" Dallas Page and more!
title: WCW Clash of The Champions XXXIII
